Task Description:
## Description

Currently, additional tags added to VPC and subnet resources outside the module will be _remove_ when re-apply, even there's no change to the network topology. To prevent tags from removal unexpectedly, this PR added lifecycle `ignore_changes` to `tags` for resource `aws_vpc` and `aws_subnet`.

Steps to reproduce the behavior:

- Applied any of the [example](https://github.com/terraform-aws-modules/terraform-aws-vpc/tree/master/examples/simple)
- Manually add tags to the VPC and subnets created by this module. This simulate an external process (eg. INFOSEC) adding additional tags.
